---
title: Lamb Meatball Sliders with Tomato Spring Salad
description: These burgers may seem tiny, but they pack a flavorful punch! Rich marinara sauce, gooey mozzarella and soft buns combine to make the perfect lamb meatball slider. Best part? You can eat more than one!
